ZH: 山梁是山脉中最高的部分。
EN: The ridge is the highest part of the mountain range.

ZH: 这座山梁被云雾所覆盖。
EN: The ridge is covered with clouds and mist.

ZH: 我们需要越过这座山梁才能到达目的地。
EN: We need to cross over this ridge to reach our destination.

ZH: 他们在山梁上搭起了帐篷。
EN: They set up a tent on the ridge.

ZH: 这座山梁提供了壮丽的景色。
EN: The ridge offers a magnificent view.

ZH: 山梁周围有很多野花。
EN: There are many wildflowers around the ridge.

ZH: 我们一直沿着山梁行进。
EN: We have been walking along the ridge.

ZH: 山梁上的空气非常清新。
EN: The air on the ridge is very fresh.

ZH: 他喜欢在山梁上散步。
EN: He enjoys taking walks on the ridge.

ZH: 山梁上的风很凉爽。
EN: The wind on the ridge is pleasantly cool.

ZH: 我们在山梁上看到了一只鹰在翱翔。
EN: We saw an eagle soaring in the sky on the ridge.

ZH: 他们在山梁上安营扎寨。
EN: They made camp on the ridge.

ZH: 我们已经爬到了山梁的最高峰。
EN: We have reached the peak of the ridge.

ZH: 逆风沿着山梁进展非常困难。
EN: It is very challenging to make progress against the wind on the ridge.

ZH: 在山梁上能够看到远处的村庄。
EN: You can see the distant village from the ridge.

ZH: 我们在山梁上发现了一条小溪。
EN: We found a small stream on the ridge.

ZH: 这座山梁是徒步旅行者的天堂。
EN: The ridge is a paradise for hikers.

ZH: 山梁上有许多供游客休息的铺子。
EN: There are many rest stops for tourists on the ridge.

ZH: 我们经过了一座狭窄的山梁。
EN: We crossed a narrow ridge.

ZH: 他们在山梁上发现了一座古老的庙宇。
EN: They discovered an ancient temple on the ridge.
